    dc:title "New material of Incadelphys antiquus (Pucadelphyda, Metatheria, Mammalia) from the early Palaeocene of Bolivia reveals phylogenetic affinities with enigmatic North and South American metatherians" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795411>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795413>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795417>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795421>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795423>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795427>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795429>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795431>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795437>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795439> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795411>
    dc:description "FIG. 2. — Incadelphys antiquus, holotype, YPFB Pal 6251 (SEM photo of cast): A, left maxillary with P1-P2, dP3, M1-M2; M3, missing the protocone, erupting; B, right maxillary with dP3, M1-M2, M3 erupting; C, right dentary with p3, dp3, m1-m2, m3 missing the trigonid, m4 in crypt. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795411/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795413>
    dc:description "FIG. 3. — Incadelphys antiquus, MHNC 13906, partial skull with dentaries: A, ventral view; B, dorsal view; C, left lateral view; D, right lateral view; E, right dentary in lateral view; F, left dentary in lateral view. Scale bar: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795413/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795417>
    dc:description "FIG. 4. — Incadelphys antiquus, MHNC 13906: A, stereopair of the right maxilla and upper tooth row in occlusal view. Scale bar: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795417/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795421>
    dc:description "FIG. 5. — Incadelphys antiquus, MHNC 13906:A, lateral view of the right upper tooth row; B, lateral view of the left upper tooth row.Scale bar:5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795421/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795423>
    dc:description "FIG. 6. — Incadelphys antiquus, MHNC 13906: A, stereopair of the left lower tooth row in occlusal view; B, stereopair of the right lower tooth row in occlusal view. Scale bar: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795423/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795427>
    dc:description "FIG. 7. — Incadelphys antiquus, MHNC 13906: A, lateral view of the right lower tooth row; B, medial view of the right lower tooth row; C, lateral view of the left lower tooth row; D, medial view of the left lower tooth row. Scale bar: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795427/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795429>
    dc:description "FIG. 8. — Incadelphys antiquus, MHNC 13906:A, dorsal view of the anterior skull;B, ventral view of the anterior skull.Scale bar:5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795429/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795431>
    dc:description "FIG. 9. — Incadelphys antiquus, MHNC 13906: A, left lateral view of the anterior skull. Scale bar: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795431/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795437>
    dc:description "FIG. 10. — Incadelphys antiquus, MHNC 13906: A, lateral view of the right dentary; B, medial view of the right dentary;C, lateral view of the left dentary;D, medial view of the left dentary; E, ventral view of the left dentary. Scale bar: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795437/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6795439>
    dc:description "FIG. 11. — Occlusal view of the M1 of some basal metatherians discussed in text showing the distolabial extension of the metastylar lobe: A, Aenigmadelphys (OMNH 22898),SEM photo of cast; B, Incadelphys (YPFB Pal 6251), SEM photo of cast; C, Incadelphys (MHNC 13906); D, Marmosopsis (MNHN.F.ITB83). Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6795439/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

